data.description: Have you been looking for a home with a POOL? Somewhere to spend your summer days and nights? Look no more! This property is a very spacious, single-story home with an open concept. A Flex space available upon entering the home. Perfect for a game room, TV Room or Office. Primary bedroom spacious with a beautiful view to the backyard. Secondary rooms are on the opposite side of the house making this home perfect for a multi-generational family. The home has recessed lights throughout allowing for an elevated feel. Large, covered patio with ceiling fans to enjoy entertaining your guests comfortably. Come check this BEAUTY out and schedule your appt.
